name: Feeding rhythms of the common goby Pomatoschistus microps at the brackish tidal marsh 'Het verdronken land van Saeftinge' in 1994
description: Catch data and numerical and gravimetrical analysis of stomach contents of Pomatoschistus microps sampled on 16, 17and 19 August 1994 at 'Het verdronken land van Saeftinge'. The datawere digitized by VLIZ fromtheoriginal report: Bulayi, M.E. (1997). Diurnal and semi lunarfeeding rhythms of thecommon goby Pomatoschistus microps in the brackishtidal marsh 'Het verdronken land van Saeftinge [sic]' (Westerschelde, SW Netherlands). MSc Thesis.
